<title>REPUBLIC OF IRELAND: EMU pact shows euro will be hard currency - Waigel.</title>
<headline>EMU pact shows euro will be hard currency - Waigel.</headline>
<dateline>DUBLIN 1996-12-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>German Finance Minister Theo Waigel said on Friday the stability pact agreed by European Union leaders showed that the single EU currency would be a hard currency.</p>
<p>&quot;The stability pact is a credible signal that the euro will be a hard currency,&quot; he said.</p>
</text>
